{"tid":2001082,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透 : 美國加快將供應鏈從中国撤走","createTime":"2020-05-04T09:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T14:42:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":423,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7e40fe82f3b59de43b2fbaf9ae17c1d54ea976","tid":2001082,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"據《路透社》引述美國官員報道，美國政府正在加快將全球工業供應鏈從中國撤走的計劃，顯示總統特朗普試圖在11月3日總統大選前履行將製造業從海外帶回美國的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n現任及前任美國高級官員表示，由於疫情破壞經濟，同時亦造成大量美國人死亡，令華府加緊推動將美國的生產及供應鏈從中國轉走，稅收優惠及補貼是考慮的措施之一。<br />\n<br />\n美國助理國務卿Keith Krach表示，在過去數年美國一直在減輕對中國供應鏈的依賴，但現時已全速加快這項行動，政府亦即將就此宣布新的計劃動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1012504/3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1012504%2F3&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1q%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=e092f639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1012504/3</a>"},{"pid":"287833ee6e0eff0f7f131c22f347af6f4a222bfe","tid":2001082,"uid":231583,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"香港=波蘭<br />\n港共=波共<br />\n中共=蘇共"},{"pid":"7809e28cfcc492681754863cd4e67f8992df7fa5","tid":2001082,"uid":290883,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"睇到所有推動 中共經濟崩潰 嘅新聞 就會覺得 異常興奮！！"},{"pid":"f1579e402cbddc8dd73c1c2b43a05aa527a3cc57","tid":2001082,"uid":121146,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> IN TRUMP WE TRUST"},{"pid":"28115257d90347050920e55ac7237b807db3b78b","tid":2001082,"uid":48040,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T09:50:11.000Z","msg":"可喜可賀，中國可以專注於自己民族復興大業、不用為美國人打工了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=QL